[gd_scene load_steps=3 format=3]

; A placeable burning-ground hazard (FireZone): an Area2D that burns any Enemy body (raider
; OR ally) overlapping it every `tick` seconds via the shared Enemy.apply_hit path, so the
; flames can actually kill. Drop it in a level and resize the CollisionShape2D / tune `burn_dmg`
; and `tick` — one scene, many fires (a burning deck, a torched field, a wall of flame).
; collision_mask = 4 = layer 3 "enemies" (raider AND ally bodies share that layer).

